{"tid":925772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為討佳人歡心登記捐骨髓　救了病童還抱得美人歸","createTime":"2018-12-03T03:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T07:06:15.000Z","uid":121473,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37e483cf5f2be62bdbc89cd0933412db758b6ea0","tid":925772,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JUmknn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JUmknn.jpg&h=274969e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希金斯捐贈骨髓救活了克羅斯，而且抱得美人歸翻攝《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n「我不太相信因果報應，但最終大家都有個愉快結局，實在太好了。」英國一名29歲男子得知心儀的女同事登記當骨髓捐贈者後，為討佳人歡心決定一同登記，沒想到他的骨髓與一名病童吻合，男童接受移植後痊癒，男子亦娶得美人歸。<br />\n <br />\n在投資銀行三菱日聯（MUFG）工作的希金斯（Billy Higgins），7年前暗戀女同事威利斯（Kate Willis），決定與對方一同參與骨髓捐贈者招募活動，「我們之前聊過天，我當時覺得是深入認識她的好機會，也在想如果加入活動，定可在她心中留下好印象。」<br />\n <br />\n希金斯的這一步不單為自己「加分」，更拯救了現年10歲的男童克羅斯（Rupert Cross）。克羅斯2014年不時頭痛求醫，2年後確診罹患骨髓增生異常症候群（myelodysplastic syndrome），這病會令骨髓製造不成熟細胞而非紅血球，有可能轉化成白血病，或令免疫系統惡化進而危及生命。<br />\n <br />\n克羅斯家人與他的骨髓並不吻合無法捐贈，不過希金斯就是合適的捐贈者，並在2016年6月完成移植手術。2年過去，克羅斯現已痊癒並可上學，「我覺得很幸運......，無法相信有人會捐骨髓給我」。<br />\n <br />\n希金斯上月與克羅斯一家見面，並向對方轉達另一個喜訊－－他與威利斯結婚了。<br />\n克羅斯母親十分感謝希金斯，「這是個奇妙的故事，他（希金斯）參加只因他喜歡的女孩也在那裡，要不是威利斯，這一切都不會發生。現在他們結婚了......，這故事很瘋狂。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181203/1477161/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181203%2F1477161%2F&d=T4XM9PkblQOSe8zhi732TU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f1b809a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181203%2F1477161%2F&h=df71589c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181203/1477161/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c9e8c2d66b0985137c148bb6f6d3819b077def","tid":925772,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c895aba10b474f33c8d71a2a72b2d17d813eb6c7","tid":925772,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"gooded<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7497459e0200c79b4e17c02eb0975aed9e4fad","tid":925772,"uid":121473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"真係好人好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b647c98985e73153c941fdcd4b98e44da3917","tid":925772,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"拍戲咁拍"},{"pid":"0126bfea172ef9b14be8b6a83f312922c4cf7f89","tid":925772,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"我都願意拎骨髓識個老婆返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}